data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom + den & loft, 2.5 bath home boasting an impressive 2,306 square feet of living space. The new wood flooring and fresh paint throughout the home make this home move-in ready. This home also offers the convenience of a bonus den when you enter the home and a loft on the second floor. Outside, the property boasts a well-maintained yard whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this backyard oasis provides the ideal setting overlooking the greenbelt. Large two car garage with one side double long. Walking distance to downtown Everett and a quick drive to the waterfront!
